    "type": "message",
    "text": "(Noticed that \"animation\" gets some extra frames on load... that points to a weakness, or tradeoff. I tried to optimize for sending every change through the graph, but that means that things like this need some kind of gate to open and close. That's a common pattern in Puredata, which I was using for some projects while making Meemoo.)",
